---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Us | Sheepdog Cyber Defense" description="Learn about Sheepdog Cyber Defense, a veteran-owned penetration testing company serving Bulverde, Spring Branch, and San Antonio." showMatrix={true}>
  <section>
    <h1>About Sheepdog Cyber Defense</h1>
    <p class="lead">We're a veteran-owned penetration testing company based in the Texas Hill Country, serving businesses throughout Bulverde, Spring Branch, San Antonio, and the surrounding areas.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Founded in 2022, Sheepdog Cyber Defense was built on a simple idea: businesses deserve clear, honest security testing without the jargon and upselling. We started to provide the kind of testing we'd want for our own organizations.</p>
    <p>As veterans, we bring discipline, thoroughness, and a get-the-job-done attitude to every engagement.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>We test systems the way attackers think—not just running automated tools and calling it a day. Every finding is verified. Every report is written to be understood by both technical and non-technical stakeholders.</p>
    <p>We'd rather tell you things are secure when they are than sell you problems you don't have.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Certifications</h2>
    <div class="certs-grid">
      <div class="cert">
        <img src="https://images.contentstack.io/v3/assets/blt36c2e63521272fdc/bltc338fb0d9bc00d53/63c71c175291cc643f1f1704/GWAPT.png" alt="GWAPT" class="cert-logo">
        <span class="cert-abbr">GWAPT</span>
        <span class="cert-full">GIAC Web Application Penetration Tester</span>
        <span class="cert-provider">SANS Institute</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cert">
        <img src="https://certifications.tcm-sec.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/PNPT-certification.webp" alt="PNPT" class="cert-logo">
        <span class="cert-abbr">PNPT</span>
        <span class="cert-full">Practical Network Penetration Tester</span>
        <span class="cert-provider">TCM Security</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cert">
        <img src="https://certifications.tcm-sec.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PWPP.webp" alt="PWPP" class="cert-logo">
        <span class="cert-abbr">PWPP</span>
        <span class="cert-full">Practical Web Pentest Professional</span>
        <span class="cert-provider">TCM Security</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cert">
        <img src="https://certifications.tcm-sec.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PWPA.webp" alt="PWPA" class="cert-logo">
        <span class="cert-abbr">PWPA</span>
        <span class="cert-full">Practical Web Pentest Associate</span>
        <span class="cert-provider">TCM Security</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cert">
        <img src="https://www.pngitem.com/pimgs/m/0-2605_certified-ethical-hacker-logo-hd-png-download.png" alt="CEH" class="cert-logo">
        <span class="cert-abbr">CEH</span>
        <span class="cert-full">Certified Ethical Hacker</span>
        <span class="cert-provider">EC-Council</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cert">
        <img src="https://wtroy.house/CRTO.png" alt="CRTO" class="cert-logo">
        <span class="cert-abbr">CRTO</span>
        <span class="cert-full">Certified Red Team Operator</span>
        <span class="cert-provider">ZeroPoint Security</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cert">
        <img src="https://www.aminbohio.com/ecppt.png" alt="eCPPTv2" class="cert-logo">
        <span class="cert-abbr">eCPPTv2</span>
        <span class="cert-full">Certified Professional Penetration Tester</span>
        <span class="cert-provider">eLearnSecurity</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Service Area</h2>
    <p>We proudly serve businesses throughout the Texas Hill Country and Greater San Antonio region, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Bulverde</li>
      <li>Spring Branch</li>
      <li>San Antonio</li>
      <li>New Braunfels</li>
      <li>Canyon Lake</li>
      <li>Boerne</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We're happy to discuss engagements outside these areas as well.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
    <p>Whether you know exactly what you need or just want to chat about security, we're here.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 700px; }
  section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  
  .certs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .cert {
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .cert-logo {
    height: 80px;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .cert-logo-text {
    height: 36px;
    width: fit-content;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-family: monospace;
  }
  
  .cert-abbr {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  
  .cert-full {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  .cert-provider {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  
  .cta {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
